			</p>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 max-w-md mx-auto gap-12 md:gap-16 pt-8">
				<div class="fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
					<div class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl text-sand mb-4">
						+23 points
					</div>
					<p class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl text-warmgray-300">
						d'activation
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
